ğŸ‘‰ Save this â€” weâ€™ll need it in Grafana.

ğŸ”¹ Step 2: Configure Grafana Contact Point (Teams)

In Grafana, go to Alerting â†’ Contact points â†’ New contact point.
Name it: Teams-Alerts.
In the Integration dropdown, select Webhook.
